	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />So, would this be the complete list of "units" inside a 2A03?
<br />
<br />- MOS Technology 6502
<br />- Low frequency timer
<br />- 2 rectangle wave generators
<br />- Triangle wave generator
<br />- Noise generator
<br />- DMC
<br />- DMA controller
<br />
<br />By the way, I don't see where the term APU fits on. I mean, is it a grouping term for those audio oriented units (and their registers) inside a 2A03?
<br />
<br />Thx.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


