	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />More evidence about zero page being just as fast internally is that on the 65816 you can set zero page anywhere in memory, and it's just as fast (as long as you put it on a 256-byte boundary).

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


