	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Author:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>Disch</b> [ Fri Apr 06, 2007 5:13 pm ]</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Enabling NMIs from a disabled state ($2000.7 goes from 0-&gt;1) when $2002.7 is set triggers an NMI.
<br />
<br />Just like $2002.7 going from 0-&gt;1 when $2000.7 triggers one.
<br />
<br />I don't know if any games rely on this behavior.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


